				</div>
				<div class="badge-content">
					<h3>Technische Unie</h3>
					<p>Officieel lid van de Technische Unie Nederland</p>
					<div class="badge-status active">Actief</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="badge-item stagger-item">
				<div class="badge-icon">
					<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M9 12l2 2m0 0l4-4m-4 4l4-4" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="badge-content">
					<h3>ISO 9001</h3>
					<p>Kwaliteitsmanagement systeem certificering</p>
