				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="badge-item stagger-item">
				<div class="badge-icon">
					<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 2L19 7V11.5C19 16.5 16 20.5 12 22C8 20.5 5 16.5 5 11.5V7L12 2Z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="badge-content">
					<h3>Security Expert</h3>
					<p>Erkend beveiligingsspecialist niveau 4</p>
					<div class="badge-status active">Geverifieerd</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="badge-item stagger-item">
				<div class="badge-icon">
					<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M21 16V8C21 6.89543 20.1046 6 19 6H5C3.89543 6 3 6.89543 3 8V16C3 17.1046 3.89543 18 5 18H19C20.1046 18 21 17.1046 21 16Z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="badge-content">
					<h3>HikVision Partner</h3>
					<p>Officieel HikVision certified partner</p>
