				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="badge-item stagger-item">
				<div class="badge-icon">
					<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke="#25c1ce" stroke-width="2"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="badge-content">
					<h3>Cameras.nl</h3>
					<p>Premium dealer van Cameras Nederland</p>
					<div class="badge-status active">Premium</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="badge-item stagger-item">
				<div class="badge-icon">
					<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
